    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>退伍军人的开疆拓土</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在 XERXES:SHADOW 中，玩家将扮演一位名叫所罗门的老兵，他发现自己正陷入一场超乎想象的星际冲突。利用你的战斗本能开始冒险，在一个即将转变的星系中航行。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3254200/extras/13907d0bf994a0f42ecbe59689c90b73.poster.avif?t=1738685631\" width=620 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3254200/extras/13907d0bf994a0f42ecbe59689c90b73.webm?t=1738685631\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3254200/extras/13907d0bf994a0f42ecbe59689c90b73.mp4?t=1738685631\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>外星人纽带：</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着你完成各种具有挑战性的任务，你会发现与外星人的神秘联系，这将重塑你对宇宙的理解。当你为生存和理解而战时，这种独特的纽带既是你最大的资产，也是你最令人困惑的挑战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>多样化的游戏玩法：从个人战斗到舰队指挥</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >XERXES:SHADOW 无缝融合了激烈的太空战斗、探索、FPS 和战略舰队指挥的玩法。驾驶您的三叉戟穿越耀眼的星云和危险的小行星带，与 Neonites 外星人展开惊心动魄的混战，并解决复杂的谜题，揭开您新发现的外星人秘密。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3254200/extras/4f872c7114e715583fbbf6a71d654595.poster.avif?t=1738685631\" width=620 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3254200/extras/4f872c7114e715583fbbf6a71d654595.webm?t=1738685631\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3254200/extras/4f872c7114e715583fbbf6a71d654595.mp4?t=1738685631\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着故事通过丰富的角色互动和戏剧性的情节转折展开，您将从一名雇佣兵一步步发展为舰队指挥官。在自己的战斗机上参加战斗的同时，向不断壮大的舰队发出实时命令，您的战术决策和驾驶技能会决定每次战斗的结果。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3254200/extras/00683bf7882ee911f611756d65e0ba64.poster.avif?t=1738685631\" width=620 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3254200/extras/00683bf7882ee911f611756d65e0ba64.webm?t=1738685631\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3254200/extras/00683bf7882ee911f611756d65e0ba64.mp4?t=1738685631\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这个史诗般的太空传奇中，不仅需要揭开古老的谜团，建立联盟，还需要面对考验您决心的道德困境。人类新领土的命运悬而未决，您的行动将决定未来的进程。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
